00:57.400 --> 00:59.300
JOE:
Crisis averted.

00:59.800 --> 01:02.300
All eyes under the age
of nine are closed.

01:02.300 --> 01:03.900
And, miracle of miracles,

01:04.500 --> 01:06.600
the children they
belong to are asleep.

01:08.000 --> 01:09.300
What about Ariel?

01:09.600 --> 01:12.000
What about Ariel?
Let's leave Ariel alone.

01:12.300 --> 01:15.300
She's 14. She's in her room
simultaneously doing homework,

01:15.300 --> 01:17.400
listening to music,
texting her friends

01:17.400 --> 01:20.400
and counting the hours
until she's 18.

01:20.400 --> 01:23.900
Let's not unnecessarily
tax her concentration.

01:24.000 --> 01:25.700
How long was I asleep?

01:26.100 --> 01:28.200
I was only gone ten minutes.
You fell asleep?

01:28.600 --> 01:30.100
I had a dream. This girl,

01:30.100 --> 01:32.400
she was in a car.
She hit a deer.

01:32.400 --> 01:34.200
She was trapped inside.

01:35.200 --> 01:36.600
Is there anyone to notify?

01:37.500 --> 01:39.500
Did you catch
the plate number?

01:40.500 --> 01:41.000
You have any idea

01:41.000 --> 01:42.900
where the accident
might have taken place?

01:42.900 --> 01:44.300
No. Nothing.

01:44.500 --> 01:46.500
I didn't even
see the girl's face.

01:46.600 --> 01:48.400
Okay. Well,
I guess there's not much

01:48.400 --> 01:50.200
to do about it right now, then.

01:51.200 --> 01:52.200
(groaning)
A little help.

01:54.200 --> 01:56.000
Anyway, you were
telling me about this woman.

01:56.500 --> 01:59.000
From Ameritips.
Cynthia Keener.

01:59.200 --> 02:02.100
Why is she paying you?
Why isn't the company that
she works for paying you?

02:02.100 --> 02:03.600
Because I don't work
for that company.

02:03.600 --> 02:05.800
She doesn't want
the company knowing
anything about me.

02:07.900 --> 02:09.600
 <i>You know, in a lot of ways,</i>
 <i>it's kind of like what I used</i>

02:09.600 --> 02:10.800
to do for Devalos.

02:11.900 --> 02:13.900
That was secret.
This is secret.

02:14.100 --> 02:15.200
But why?

02:16.900 --> 02:18.700
I think the job
is all she has.

02:18.700 --> 02:22.100
I think she wants to impress
the people that she works for.

02:22.100 --> 02:23.300
I guess she's hoping
I'll be able

02:23.300 --> 02:25.500
to help her
with some of her cases.

02:25.600 --> 02:27.200
Give her a leg up.

02:27.900 --> 02:32.800
She'll get the glory,
I'll get the 800 bucks a week.

